TextGraph-TransCLIP is an independent research extension inspired by:

1. K. El Khoury et al., "Enhancing Remote Sensing Vision-Language Models for Zero-Shot Scene Classification," ICASSP 2025.
   Official code: https://github.com/elkhouryk/RS-TransCLIP

2. M. Zanella, B. Gérin, and I. Ben Ayed, "Boosting Vision-Language Models with Transduction," NeurIPS 2024.

The prompt inventory follows the public RS-TransCLIP repository. The TextGraph implementation rewrites the graph construction and solver integration for this repository. Retain the original attributions and comply with checkpoint and dataset licenses when redistributing derived resources.
